no_spell
6-13-96 Bp
 
Two ways to prevent casting of basic spells,
(basic spells are: fi,sh,so,mi, and invis)

1)an object on the player with an id of no_spell will stop players from casting

2) Calling set_spell_block(1); in the player object does the same.
 
the blocking status may be found with query_spell_block();
